40:50.448 --> 40:52.319
I-I don't know how to thank you.

40:52.362 --> 40:54.495
Get help. That's all
the thanks I need.

40:54.539 --> 40:56.236
I'm going
to a meeting tonight.

40:56.279 --> 40:57.411
Well, that's
a good start.

40:57.455 --> 40:59.108
And I-I've got
an interview tomorrow

40:59.152 --> 41:00.501
at another stable.

41:00.545 --> 41:02.851
It's just as a stable hand
for now,

41:02.895 --> 41:05.854
but I'll be around horses,
